83     ////////////////////////////////////////////////////////////////////////////////
84     /// @brief  MM32 MCU Interrupt Handle
85     ////////////////////////////////////////////////////////////////////////////////
86     typedef enum IRQn {
87         NonMaskableInt_IRQn             = -14,                                  ///< 2 Non Maskable Interrupt
88         HardFault_IRQn                  = -13,                                  ///< 3 Cortex-M0 Hard Fault Interrupt
89         SVC_IRQn                        = -5,                                   ///< 11 Cortex-M0 SV Call Interrupt
90         PendSV_IRQn                     = -2,                                   ///< 14 Cortex-M0 Pend SV Interrupt
91         SysTick_IRQn                    = -1,                                   ///< 15 Cortex-M0 System Tick Interrupt
92         WWDG_IWDG_IRQn                  = 0,                                    ///< WatchDog Interrupt
93         WWDG_IRQn                       = 0,                                    ///< Window WatchDog Interrupt
94         PVD_IRQn                        = 1,                                    ///< PVD through EXTI Line detect Interrupt
95         BKP_IRQn                        = 2,                                    ///< RTC through EXTI Line Interrupt
96         RTC_IRQn                        = 2,                                    ///< RTC through EXTI Line Interrupt
97         FLASH_IRQn                      = 3,                                    ///< FLASH Interrupt
98         RCC_IRQn                        = 4,                                    ///< RCC Interrupt
99         EXTI0_1_IRQn                    = 5,                                    ///< EXTI Line 0 and 1 Interrupts
100         EXTI2_3_IRQn                    = 6,                                    ///< EXTI Line 2 and 3 Interrupts
101         EXTI4_15_IRQn                   = 7,                                    ///< EXTI Line 4 to 15 Interrupts
102         DMA1_Channel1_IRQn              = 9,                                    ///< DMA1 Channel 1 Interrupt
103         DMA1_Channel2_3_IRQn            = 10,                                   ///< DMA1 Channel 2 and Channel 3 Interrupts
104         DMA1_Channel4_5_IRQn            = 11,                                   ///< DMA1 Channel 4 and Channel 5 Interrupts
105         ADC_IRQn                        = 12,                                   ///< ADC Interrupts
106         ADC1_IRQn                       = 12,                                   ///< ADC Interrupts
107         TIM1_BRK_UP_TRG_COM_IRQn        = 13,                                   ///< TIM1 Break, Update, Trigger and Commutation Interrupts
108         TIM1_CC_IRQn                    = 14,                                   ///< TIM1 Capture Compare Interrupt
109         TIM2_IRQn                       = 15,                                   ///< TIM2 Interrupt
110         TIM3_IRQn                       = 16,                                   ///< TIM3 Interrupt
111         TIM14_IRQn                      = 19,                                   ///< TIM14 Interrupt
112         TIM16_IRQn                      = 21,                                   ///< TIM16 Interrupt
113         TIM17_IRQn                      = 22,                                   ///< TIM17 Interrupt
114         I2C1_IRQn                       = 23,                                   ///< I2C1 Interrupt
115         SPI1_IRQn                       = 25,                                   ///< SPI1 Interrupt
116         SPI2_IRQn                       = 26,                                   ///< SPI1 Interrupt
117         UART1_IRQn                      = 27,                                   ///< UART1 Interrupt
118         UART2_IRQn                      = 28,                                   ///< UART2 Interrupt
119     } IRQn_Type;

478     ////////////////////////////////////////////////////////////////////////////////
479     /// @brief EXTI Registers Structure Definition
480     ////////////////////////////////////////////////////////////////////////////////
481     typedef struct {
482         __IO u32 CFGR;                                                              ///< configuration register,                        offset: 0x00
483         u32 Reserved;                                                               ///< Reserved                                       offset: 0x04
484         __IO u32 CR[4];                                                             ///< External interrupt configuration register,     offset: 0x08 - 0x17

489         __IO u32 RTSR;                                                              ///< Rising Trigger Status Register                 offset: 0x08 + 0x400
490         __IO u32 FTSR;                                                              ///< Falling Trigger Status Register                offset: 0x0C + 0x400

492         __IO u32 PR;                                                                ///< Pending Register                               offset: 0x14 + 0x400
493     } EXTI_TypeDef;

987             __IO u32 SCSR;
988         };
989         union {

991             __IO u32 EXTCTL;
992         };
993     } SPI_TypeDef;
